    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_31_5373-5469",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "5373-5469",
      "markText": "简而言之，理想国中各个阶级、各个群体都应从事顺应各自天性和禀赋的工作；阶级间、个体间互不干扰，却又通过不同的分工相互配合，形成一个高效、和谐的整体。（第433—434节）这就是一个公正的国度。",
      "totalCount": 1456,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5373&rangeEnd=5469",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=5373&rangeEnd=5469"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_22_376-443",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "376-443",
      "markText": "哲学使人愉悦，即使是形而上学的幻景也蕴含诱惑，每个学习者都能体会得到，直到粗粝的生存需求将我们从思想的高峰拽下，抛入生活的撕扯琐碎中。",
      "totalCount": 1241,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=376&rangeEnd=443",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=376&rangeEnd=443"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_30_3039-3079",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "3039-3079",
      "markText": "有个更好的办法，那就是赋予社会道德约束以超自然的权威和制裁力量。我们必须有宗教。",
      "totalCount": 1216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=3039&rangeEnd=3079",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=3039&rangeEnd=3079"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_28_2824-2880",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2824-2880",
      "markText": "设法阻止没能力和不诚实的人靠近公共权力，挑选并培养最优秀的统治者来服务公共利益——这就是政治哲学所要考虑的问题。",
      "totalCount": 1012,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2824&rangeEnd=2880",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2824&rangeEnd=2880"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_27_1871-1938",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "1871-1938",
      "markText": "一个真正会生活的人能将他的欲望充分发挥和表现出来，但当这些欲望增长到最大限度时，他又能用勇气和智慧来调控它们，并同时满足他所有的渴望。",
      "totalCount": 960,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=1871&rangeEnd=1938",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=1871&rangeEnd=1938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_32_609-647",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "609-647",
      "markText": "而对于正义，柏拉图勇敢地给出了他的定义：“正义就是人人各得其所，各尽其责。”",
      "totalCount": 960,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=609&rangeEnd=647",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=609&rangeEnd=647"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_56_17815-17857",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "17815-17857",
      "markText": "伟大并不是凌驾于人类之上统治他人，而是站在无知的欲望所滋生的偏颇和无益之上统领自己。",
      "totalCount": 960,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=17815&rangeEnd=17857",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=17815&rangeEnd=17857"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_28_2295-2334",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2295-2334",
      "markText": "要使一种学说被接受或否定，只需要在当下受欢迎的戏剧中对其进行一番赞扬或嘲讽即可",
      "totalCount": 930,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2295&rangeEnd=2334",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2295&rangeEnd=2334"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_27_2749-2784",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "2749-2784",
      "markText": "什么是正义？——我们应该追求正义，还是权力？——善良与强大，哪个更好？",
      "totalCount": 901,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=2749&rangeEnd=2784",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=2749&rangeEnd=2784"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_31_3584-3663",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "3584-3663",
      "markText": "社会分工根据的是每个人的天资和能力，而非性别；如果一个女人展示出政治管理的能力，那么就让她来统治；如果一个男人表现得只会洗盘子，那么就让他顺应天意，恪尽职守。",
      "totalCount": 876,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=3584&rangeEnd=3663",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=3584&rangeEnd=3663"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_31_1195-1242",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "1195-1242",
      "markText": "天才不管诞生在哪儿，美好的前程总是在等待着他。这是教育的民主——比选举式民主诚实和有效一百倍。",
      "totalCount": 846,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1195&rangeEnd=1242",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1195&rangeEnd=1242"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_20_6263-6282",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "6263-6282",
      "markText": "通往知识的大道没有近路可抄，这是真理。",
      "totalCount": 836,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=6263&rangeEnd=6282",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=6263&rangeEnd=6282"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_37_3259-3331",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "3259-3331",
      "markText": "我们身上总是保留着许多为我们自己所谴责的东西：就像只有相似之处才能拿来做比较，相似之人才会争吵，最剧烈的争战也往往源于意图或信仰上最细微的差异。",
      "totalCount": 799,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=3259&rangeEnd=3331",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=3259&rangeEnd=3331"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_42_10344-10424",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "10344-10424",
      "markText": "国家所追求的目标应该由公众来决定，但实现它的途径只能由专家来决定和执行；选择的权利应该以民主的方式广泛散布，但政府职务只能严格地由具备条件并且经过筛选的人担当。",
      "totalCount": 793,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=10344&rangeEnd=10424",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=10344&rangeEnd=10424"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_32_1407-1469",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "1407-1469",
      "markText": "正义不仅指力量，而且指一种和谐的力量——欲望归于秩序形成智慧，人民归于秩序形成组织；正义不是强者的权力，而是整体的有效协作。",
      "totalCount": 782,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1407&rangeEnd=1469",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1407&rangeEnd=1469"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23783430_20_5843-5866",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "5843-5866",
      "markText": "因为清楚明白地表达正是哲学家最不该具备的品质。",
      "totalCount": 780,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23783430&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5843&rangeEnd=5866",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5832af0716ae806e581eab?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5843&rangeEnd=5866"
    },
    {
